    lastUpdated: 'August 25, 2021',
    summary: 'In-depth investigation of Social Media Radicalization Pipeline drawing on declassified materials, court records, congressional testimony, and financial disclosures. The documented evidence reveals systematic institutional failures demanding accountability.',
